prompts.frontCover: Vibrant, flat 2D illustration for a greeting card. A dreamy, fantasy mountain scene under a soft, pastel twilight sky with glowing stars. In a humorous and lighthearted scenario, illustrated characters of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are snowboarding down a snowy, fantastical mountain slope. Lao Lao, in her white ruffled dress, expertly balances on her snowboard with a playful, triumphant expression, one arm raised in the air. Jordan, in his graduation gown (but without the sash, tie, or hat), comically tumbles backwards off his snowboard in a flurry of snow, with a surprised but amused look on his face. Racing alongside them down the slope are two adorable cartoon Corgis, also on tiny snowboards, wearing little helmets and looking thrilled. The mountains are whimsical, with pastel purple and pink snow, and the trees are stylized and sparkly. The entire scene has a magical, ethereal glow with soft light and sparkling motes floating in the air. Centered in a clear area of the pastel sky, the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script.
